creator.description:
Labeling service for #Medsky to identify medical specialties, created by @wcima.bsky.social and @richardferro.bsky.social

INSTRUCTIONS:
1. SUBSCRIBE to labeler
2. LIKE the post with desired specialty
3. ENJOY!
X. REMOVE badge by liking “remove” post
